com.architech.spm.services
Class Dashboards

java.lang.Object
  com.architech.spm.services.Dashboards

public class Dashboards
extends java.lang.Object

A service class that provides methods related to dashboards, including the dashboard definitions, alerts, and support articles. This service class is exposed using JAX-WS and is named SPM Dashboards in the application server.

Author:
nate

Method Detail

listDashboards

public java.util.ArrayList<DashboardDefinition> listDashboards()
Returns a list of all dashboards (primary plus windows) defined for the current user's role. If a dashboard has been created for this specific user, it will replace the role-specific dashboard, and the role-specific dashboard will not be returned.

Returns:
A list of user-specific dashboards
